ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"高尚情操可能都會話 <br />\n藍屍愛國愛黨 本具高尚情操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4711d7a610fd8cfde9fae39785ef843887a30a","tid":2234492,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:05:14.000Z","msg":"推 踢爆港府密謀12人送中　 警務人員坐定翼機　監視偷渡艇 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2234291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2234291</a>"},{"pid":"00e80fc90b428903fbf795180c4afa4d29fa157a","tid":2234492,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:06:52.000Z","msg":"夠疆咪放上高院等陪審團判囉<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"da187ff10b3d58914270648b95d2baf3bfdfb903","tid":2234492,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:07:17.000Z","msg":"證明藍絲比黃絲更勤力、更敢於死纏爛打"},{"pid":"f7bbf203e95a3096915bb6fd4a3a790edfa103e0","tid":2234492,"uid":264281,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a1d265ee00ec5797a7231abd887c53c6360e6169","tid":2234492,"uid":44209,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"quote":{"pid":"e7cb4a9103b413e5dfe86fa3552c7a959c90c916","tid":2234492,"uid":51469,"like":22,"dislike":5,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"649521e74ddf31d82d2692095e2c757452106862","tid":2234492,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4dLpCo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4dLpCo.jpg&h=0a85b540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1100 #有線 <br />\n裁判官何俊堯被投訴審理八宗反修例案件時，針對警員或輕判被告，除兩案仍在上訴外，其餘投訴都不成立<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/cohesionkwuntong/8922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcohesionkwuntong%2F8922&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5EtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=ab7a7333\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/cohesionkwuntong/8922</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:05:04.000Z","msg":"係投訴不成立<br />\n定係個被告罪名不成立？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:06:15.000Z","msg":"投訴不成立"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"投訴師出動<br />\n一個個紅官投訴"},{"pid":"67b4f7d5ca92f55f0ebdaa7dcd5a3c66dc546cc3","tid":2234492,"uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a112e84ae231b66adc2d56513b0d67cc612c7b6","tid":2234492,"uid":271513,"like":91,"dislike":1,"score":90,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:08:52.000Z","msg":"咁我地投訴鄭紀航，蘇狗嗰啲又有冇理我地<br />\n<br />\n我寄左十幾封信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"蘇 入左極權法判官團, 如果投訴成立 無得審社會案, 即係推翻林奠(共)嘅委任 唔比審極權法；<br />\n如果投訴成立,唔比審社運,但又可以審極權法.真係唔知講咩好......"},{"pid":"ba017f248838be6a14b4573caf09027371ec204c","tid":2234492,"uid":121145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e4f5d9e34621c1e081852918146d3edaf1eafa","tid":2234492,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕一名支持港府、中共的八旬老翁今年4月16日於香港中聯辦附近涉嫌刺傷前立法會議員梁國雄，還高呼聲稱要「替天行道」。老翁今天（17日）在法庭上認罪，但強調是「為香港出頭」；<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">主審法官鄭紀航竟稱許犯嫌「熱愛社會」</span></span>，因與被害者政見不同才犯案，決定先為其申請社會服務令；前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒大呼這段法庭對話令人傻眼！<br />\n<br />\n綜合港媒報導，「長毛」梁國雄事發當日率眾到中聯辦請願，抗議港澳辦及中聯辦高調干預立法會事務，之後卻被81歲的黃森球以鑿刀襲擊，致使其右腰窩受傷。今天黃男於香港東區裁判法院承認一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，但強調是為香港出頭，狂言說若要有槍絕對槍擊梁國雄，還在庭上揚言「一個許智峯，一個黃之鋒，兩個遲早都要死」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n針對政治人物行兇，放喺全世界審判都應係加刑理由，而鄭紀航竟成為減刑理由，仲事先表明唔會判監禁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HMFmHNM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHMFmHNM.jpg&h=b0442d18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34761ab20b180dcb4eff53ccae179299b91a65a0","tid":2234492,"uid":48067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649521e74ddf31d82d2692095e2c757452106862","tid":2234492,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4dLpCo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4dLpCo.jpg&h=0a85b540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1100 #有線 <br />\n裁判官何俊堯被投訴審理八宗反修例案件時，針對警員或輕判被告，除兩案仍在上訴外，其餘投訴都不成立<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/cohesionkwuntong/8922\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcohesionkwuntong%2F8922&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5EtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=ab7a7333\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/cohesionkwuntong/8922</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:15:31.000Z","msg":"求投訴紅官link再投訴多次，保好官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbaefca4d88639047f83068a97802ee9c3494e4","tid":2234492,"uid":319935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b458e1f5662663b96c02734f772b6cd19db6bd57","tid":2234492,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:14:01.000Z","msg":"正 總裁判官都係偏黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有部份官係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n法治都未算死得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T04:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果法官係黃 咁法治都係要死<br />\n法官嘅天職係要公正判案 唔可以有立場<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">你前言不對後語 誤導市民大眾 我祝你跟住法治早啲死</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c86b06e79ff46a24158cd0f8bf1a0d0e9901f52","tid":2234492,"uid":141286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7bbf203e95a3096915bb6fd4a3a790edfa103e0","tid